messages.content:
**There was a giveaway running, now what?**

Heard some of you asked about that, I can't blame you, we had about 300 entries for the Giveaways, all I can say is: don't worry, we're not leaving you empty handed, there will soon be new giveaways!

**What can I do to help?**

Our team is working hard, I am working hard. A lot of you are supporting us in here or sending me private messages, and I appreciate that, this is what keeps us doing that. There's no other ways to help, we're not asking for donations, spam or such, all you can do is keep acting as you always did, respecting the rules and doing so being helpful for the community. Only thing I would like to enforce is the BackUp server, join that because this is the only way to keep going if they hit us again, here's the link: https://discord.gg/bQAE7mt

**Last but not least, I wanted to thank everyone for remaining here, for those who keep joining and supporting us. We got hit but we didn't die, we won't die until there's a reason to keep going!**

Stay safe!

@everyone **IMPORTANT ANNOUNCEMENT REGUARDING THE ACTUAL SITUATION:**

 Hey guys, as you can notice we managed to bring back most of the stuff that was in here, our main focus was to keep helping you all with your financial issues on the game and that's why we tried to take back everything as fastest as possible.

**Did anything change?**

Well pretty much nothing changed beyond the fact that we lost like 3/4 of our members, think this like a big House Moving, everything will be as it was or even better! We'll keep doing what we did, we're now stronger than before. We've worked mainly to bring back the FREE lobbies system, ensuring our service to keep going, our aim is to help all of you and this is what didn't stop us. There's some work left to do on our side but we're pretty much set up.

**What about the old roles?**

Unfortunally we didn't have any backup, dumb move not gonna lie, we had to remake every channel, bot command, embeds starting from 0, but we're doing it without too much hassle. Honestly it would be very hard to get back everyone their old "premium" roles because there were A LOT of people having those roles. I will try to atleast give back the @Donator roles to those who donated, so please, send me a message if you did and I'll verify and add the role to you, I'm not forgiving anyone, but I hope you will understand how much work there's under a "simple" discord server.

**What about "Premium" services?**

Some of you already asked me about them, things will slightly change in terms of "viewing" the stuff, we still don't know how but I'm working on it already and will soon be opening them to the public again. 
***Note that I'm still available to do any of them, but for now you should be sending me a Private Message and I'll give you all the info, because for the moment we won't have any ticket system or channel for that.***

**How to get rid of the endless loading screen (stuck in clouds) :**

> Step 1: CTRL+SHIFT+ESCAPE. (opens task manager)
> Step 2:Click on more details if not expanded already.
> Step 3:Go to performance tab.
> Step 4:Open resource monitor.
> Step 5:Go to CPU tab.
> Step 6:Right click on GTAV.exe and suspend its process.
> Step 7:After 10 seconds resume process.

**Done.**
